"contexto :class:`warnings.catch_warnings` use uma :class:`~contextvars."
"ContextVar` para armazenar o estado do filtro de avisos. Se nĂŁo definida, o "
"valor padrĂŁo desta opĂ§ĂŁo serĂĄ ``1`` em construĂ§Ă”es com threads livres e "
"``0`` em outras. Veja tambĂ©m :envvar:`PYTHON_CONTEXT_AWARE_WARNINGS`."

#: ../../using/cmdline.rst:672
msgid ""
":samp:`-X tlbc={0,1}` enables (1, the default) or disables (0) thread-local "
"bytecode in builds configured with :option:`--disable-gil`.  When disabled, "
"this also disables the specializing interpreter.  See also :envvar:"
"`PYTHON_TLBC`."
msgstr ""
":samp:`-X tlbc={0,1}` habilita (1, o padrĂŁo) ou desabilita (0) o bytecode "
"local da thread em construĂ§Ă”es configuradas com :option:`--disable-gil`. "
"Quando desabilitado, tambĂ©m desabilita o interpretador especializado. Veja "
"tambĂ©m :envvar:`PYTHON_TLBC`."

#: ../../using/cmdline.rst:679
msgid ""
"It also allows passing arbitrary values and retrieving them through the :"
"data:`sys._xoptions` dictionary."
msgstr ""
"TambĂ©m permite passar valores arbitrĂĄrios e recuperĂĄ-los atravĂ©s do "
"dicionĂĄrio :data:`sys._xoptions`."

#: ../../using/cmdline.rst:684
msgid "Removed the ``-X showalloccount`` option."
msgstr "Removida a opĂ§ĂŁo ``-X showalloccount``."

#: ../../using/cmdline.rst:687
msgid "Removed the ``-X oldparser`` option."
msgstr "Removida a opĂ§ĂŁo ``-X oldparser``."

#: ../../using/cmdline.rst:692
msgid ""
":option:`!-J` is no longer reserved for use by Jython_, and now has no "
