"``1`` em construĂ§Ă”es com threads livres e ``0`` em outras. Consulte :option:"
"`-X context_aware_warnings<-X>`."

#: ../../using/cmdline.rst:1313
msgid ""
"On builds where experimental just-in-time compilation is available, this "
